1
00:00:05,965 --> 00:00:08,633
Tukar antara versi berwarna dan hitam
putih dengan "Versi berbeza" di bawah.

2
00:00:08,634 --> 00:00:11,971
Disediakan dalam peranti yang disokong.

3
00:00:25,151 --> 00:00:27,945
<i>Seseorang pernah tanya saya
erti alam semesta ini.</i>

4
00:00:29,071 --> 00:00:32,324
<i>Saya ingat soalan aneh itu
sampai hari ini.</i>

5
00:00:33,743 --> 00:00:37,163
<i>Yang pasti, saya hanya tahu
tentang alam semesta ini.</i>

6
00:00:37,955 --> 00:00:39,957
<i>Ini benar pada waktu itu dan sekarang.</i>

7
00:00:40,374 --> 00:00:42,125
PELARANGAN
SILVERMANE UNTUNG

8
00:00:42,126 --> 00:00:44,211
<i>Adakah saya orang yang luar biasa?</i>

9
00:00:44,712 --> 00:00:45,671
<i>Ya.</i>

10
00:00:46,172 --> 00:00:47,757
<i>Adakah saya orang biasa?</i>

11
00:00:48,257 --> 00:00:49,549
<i>Ya.</i>

12
00:00:49,550 --> 00:00:50,759
<i>Saya kedua-duanya,</i>

13
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:52,177
<i>dan bukan kedua-duanya.</i>

14
00:00:52,178 --> 00:00:53,220
<i>Kita semua begitu.</i>

15
00:00:55,806 --> 00:00:56,891
<i>New York.</i>

16
00:01:00,186 --> 00:01:01,771
<i>Saya membesar di bandar ini,</i>

17
00:01:03,522 --> 00:01:05,149
<i>belajar bertempur di bandar ini…</i>

18
00:01:08,110 --> 00:01:09,820
<i>dan jatuh cinta di bandar ini.</i>

19
00:01:13,741 --> 00:01:15,367
<i>Kesilapan yang takkan diulangi.</i>

20
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:23,082
<i>Dulu saya ialah Spider,
adiwira bandar ini.</i>

21
00:01:23,083 --> 00:01:26,921
<i>Sentiasa memerhati dan bersedia
untuk menyelamatkan orang.</i>

22
00:01:44,188 --> 00:01:46,816
<i>Semua itu berakhir apabila Ruby meninggal.</i>

23
00:01:58,744 --> 00:02:00,913
<i>Kami patut berkahwin pada musim bunga.</i>

24
00:02:01,789 --> 00:02:04,874
<i>Cincin perkahwinan pun sudah dibeli,</i>

25
00:02:04,875 --> 00:02:07,253
<i>tapi saya tak berpeluang
memberinya cincin itu.</i>

26
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:10,464
{\an8}RUBY J WILLIAMS
18 DISEMBER 1890 - MEI

27
00:02:16,136 --> 00:02:21,308
<i>Ruby pernah kata kuasa yang besar
membawa tanggungjawab yang besar.</i>

28
00:02:22,518 --> 00:02:25,855
{\an8}<i>Dialah tanggungjawab terbesar saya.</i>

29
00:02:27,106 --> 00:02:28,482
<i>Saya gagal melindunginya.</i>

30
00:02:30,276 --> 00:02:32,152
<i>Spider gagal melindunginya.</i>

31
00:02:35,030 --> 00:02:39,243
<i>Selepas itu, saya tak mahu memikul kuasa
atau tanggungjawab itu lagi.</i>

32
00:02:42,746 --> 00:02:45,666
<i>Jadi, saya kembali
menjadi orang yang biasa.</i>

33
00:02:47,793 --> 00:02:50,129
<i>Itu kisah lima tahun yang lalu.</i>

34
00:04:05,788 --> 00:04:08,165
{\an8}BERDASARKAN
MARVEL COMICS

35
00:04:39,571 --> 00:04:40,614
Apa pendapat awak?

36
00:04:45,119 --> 00:04:47,286
Rasanya dia orang di dalam foto ini.

37
00:04:47,287 --> 00:04:48,955
Awak agak tampan.

38
00:04:48,956 --> 00:04:50,958
Adakah penglihatan awak bermasalah?

39
00:04:52,167 --> 00:04:53,043
Lucu juga.

40
00:04:53,919 --> 00:04:55,378
Awak ada isteri?

41
00:04:55,379 --> 00:04:57,714
- Tiada.
- Kasihan.

42
00:04:57,715 --> 00:04:59,173
Saya ada suami.

43
00:04:59,174 --> 00:05:01,342
Itu tak halang saya untuk berseronok.

44
00:05:01,343 --> 00:05:02,844
Faham maksud saya?

45
00:05:02,845 --> 00:05:04,054
Saya faham.

46
00:05:04,722 --> 00:05:07,515
Apabila suami awak juga faham,
suruh dia hubungi saya.

47
00:05:07,516 --> 00:05:09,308
B REILLY
DETEKTIF PERIBADI

48
00:05:09,309 --> 00:05:10,144
Okey.

49
00:05:14,064 --> 00:05:16,025
Maaf, encik!

50
00:05:17,026 --> 00:05:18,819
- Terlupa topi.
- Terima kasih.

51
00:05:20,237 --> 00:05:23,532
Tak baik bagi awak
jika awak terus mengekori saya.

52
00:05:24,158 --> 00:05:25,409
Selalunya begitu.

53
00:05:27,077 --> 00:05:28,370
Addison!

54
00:05:49,767 --> 00:05:50,683
Maaf, kawan.

55
00:05:50,684 --> 00:05:53,478
Hei! Jangan lakukannya, Addison.

56
00:05:53,479 --> 00:05:56,273
Saya takkan teragak-agak
untuk tembak atau kejar awak.

57
00:05:59,777 --> 00:06:00,861
Tak guna!

58
00:06:09,453 --> 00:06:12,164
- Dia okey?
- Ya Tuhan. Dia dah mati?

59
00:06:19,338 --> 00:06:21,255
Encik, jangan. Jangan…

60
00:06:21,256 --> 00:06:23,258
Mereka pergi ke mana? Arah mana?

61
00:06:31,934 --> 00:06:34,645
SYARIKAT STANDARD OIL

62
00:06:59,128 --> 00:07:01,712
Bukan salah saya
awak cari pasal dengan orang.

63
00:07:01,713 --> 00:07:05,050
Mari kita pergi. Dah lewat
dan sangat busuk di belakang sini.

64
00:07:05,592 --> 00:07:07,219
Saya dah beri amaran.

65
00:07:08,137 --> 00:07:09,138
Apa?

66
00:07:18,147 --> 00:07:19,857
Sekarang awak akan dibakar.

67
00:07:27,906 --> 00:07:29,783
Ya Tuhan!

68
00:07:35,581 --> 00:07:36,497
Alamak!

69
00:07:36,498 --> 00:07:37,332
MUDAH TERBAKAR

70
00:07:37,875 --> 00:07:39,209
Ya Tuhan!

71
00:08:07,571 --> 00:08:10,657
PATRICK DONEGAL
PENYIASAT PERIBADI

72
00:08:11,325 --> 00:08:12,534
Okey.

73
00:08:14,328 --> 00:08:16,079
Lelaki itu terbakar sepenuhnya!

74
00:08:16,705 --> 00:08:18,164
Itu mustahil.

75
00:08:18,165 --> 00:08:19,624
Saya sepatutnya dah agak.

76
00:08:19,625 --> 00:08:22,043
Mereka tawarkan 50 dolar
untuk menjejaki dia.

77
00:08:22,044 --> 00:08:24,212
Siapa upah awak? Lelaki bernama Winston?

78
00:08:24,213 --> 00:08:26,757
- Ya.
- Tawaran saya hanya 30 dolar.

79
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:30,343
Saya nak minum arak. Awak?

80
00:08:30,344 --> 00:08:33,012
Nak. Tapi jangan terlalu mahal.
Saya hanya ada…

81
00:08:33,013 --> 00:08:36,600
Tiga dolar. Mari, Donegal.
Saya tahu suatu tempat.

82
00:08:37,434 --> 00:08:40,479
Mungkin ada wanita juga
jika awak suka wanita yang malang.

83
00:08:42,064 --> 00:08:45,567
Saya pasti suka kerana
saya asyik mengahwini wanita begitu.

84
00:08:51,156 --> 00:08:53,616
- Selamat pagi.
- Pagi dah lalu.

85
00:08:53,617 --> 00:08:57,245
Sekarang sudah tengah hari
dan sedang menuju ke petang.

86
00:08:57,246 --> 00:09:00,248
- Kopi?
- Ada minuman yang lebih kuat?

87
00:09:00,249 --> 00:09:02,625
Itulah yang saya beritahu suami saya.

88
00:09:02,626 --> 00:09:05,503
- Tuangkannya ke sini saja.
- Itu dia, memang tak boleh.

89
00:09:05,504 --> 00:09:06,796
Ada panggilan?

90
00:09:06,797 --> 00:09:11,175
Untuk terima panggilan, kena bayar bil.
Jika tak, itu hanya penindih kertas.

91
00:09:11,176 --> 00:09:12,469
Bagaimana dengan Addison?

92
00:09:15,138 --> 00:09:16,265
Begitu bagus, ya?

93
00:09:17,766 --> 00:09:19,183
Addison dah mati.

94
00:09:19,184 --> 00:09:22,228
- Awak…
- Bukan, orang lain.

95
00:09:22,229 --> 00:09:24,272
Bandar tak guna ini.

96
00:09:24,273 --> 00:09:25,523
Masih buka?

97
00:09:25,524 --> 00:09:27,400
- Tak.
- Ya.

98
00:09:27,401 --> 00:09:28,401
Dah telefon, tapi…

99
00:09:28,402 --> 00:09:32,363
En. Reilly suka berurusan
secara bersemuka.

100
00:09:32,364 --> 00:09:34,615
Setuju tak, En…

101
00:09:34,616 --> 00:09:37,703
- Carmedy.
- Silakan, En. Carmedy.

102
00:09:38,537 --> 00:09:39,871
Ini tentang isteri saya.

103
00:09:50,841 --> 00:09:53,010
Awak kaya tak, En. Carmedy?

104
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:56,637
Tak. Tak begitu kaya.

105
00:09:56,638 --> 00:09:58,515
Jadi, pasti tajam akal awak.

106
00:10:02,561 --> 00:10:04,895
Saya terdengar
perbualan telefon isteri saya.

107
00:10:04,896 --> 00:10:08,316
Dia akan jumpa seseorang
pada pukul 8.00 malam ini.

108
00:10:08,317 --> 00:10:10,276
Saya bahkan ada alamatnya. Lihat.

109
00:10:10,277 --> 00:10:13,195
Saya suka klien yang buat persediaan.

110
00:10:13,196 --> 00:10:15,281
Jadi, adakah awak akan terima kes saya?

111
00:10:15,282 --> 00:10:17,616
Okey. Upah saya 10 dolar sehari, tambah…

112
00:10:17,617 --> 00:10:19,952
Tapi awak akan tangkap gambar, bukan?

113
00:10:19,953 --> 00:10:23,831
Sebab tanpa gambar, kes ini
"dia cakap, saya cakap" tiada bukti.

114
00:10:23,832 --> 00:10:26,042
Saya pasti ini salah faham saja,

115
00:10:26,043 --> 00:10:27,793
tapi jika benar, jangan risau.

116
00:10:27,794 --> 00:10:29,713
- Ben amat mahir.
- Tak pernah terlepas.

117
00:10:33,091 --> 00:10:34,008
10 dolar sehari.

118
00:10:34,009 --> 00:10:35,760
Tambah perbelanjaan.

119
00:10:35,761 --> 00:10:38,346
Janet akan catat maklumat awak
dan minta deposit.

120
00:10:38,347 --> 00:10:42,433
Datang lagi pada lusa dan saya
akan beri awak apa yang awak minta.

121
00:10:42,434 --> 00:10:43,518
Terima kasih.

122
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:47,981
Ayuh, En. Carmedy.
Berikan maklumat awak dan deposit.

123
00:10:51,568 --> 00:10:55,363
"Letupan di Standard Oil,"
baca tentangnya.

124
00:10:55,364 --> 00:10:58,532
"Letupan di Standard Oil!"

125
00:10:58,533 --> 00:11:02,287
Letupan, di sini, di Standard Oil!

126
00:11:17,636 --> 00:11:20,054
Maaf, terlewat. Saya kejar berita terkini.

127
00:11:20,055 --> 00:11:24,934
Akhirnya, ada ketua geng
yang ingin jatuhkan Silvermane.

128
00:11:24,935 --> 00:11:27,144
Dia bakar rumah agam Silvermane,

129
00:11:27,145 --> 00:11:31,065
bunuh enam konconya,
dan entah bagaimana, Silvermane selamat.

130
00:11:31,066 --> 00:11:33,526
Adakah Finn Byrne
suka dipanggil Silvermane?

131
00:11:33,527 --> 00:11:37,696
Adakah nama itu membawa erti
orang penting yang panjang umur?

132
00:11:37,697 --> 00:11:39,949
Jika saya sekaya dia,
panggil saya apa saja.

133
00:11:39,950 --> 00:11:41,952
Jeruk itu dah dimakan. Okey.

134
00:11:43,620 --> 00:11:45,956
Apa kes yang awak sembunyikan?
Kes curang lagi?

135
00:11:48,417 --> 00:11:49,708
Bukankah dah berhenti?

136
00:11:49,709 --> 00:11:53,045
Dah berbulan-bulan
saya tak bayar gaji Janet. Terpaksa.

137
00:11:53,046 --> 00:11:55,297
Awak yang memilih untuk hidup begini.

138
00:11:55,298 --> 00:11:58,301
- Aduhai, Ben.
- Robbie, sudahlah, okey? Jangan.

139
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:01,887
Nampak keadaan bandar ini?

140
00:12:01,888 --> 00:12:03,390
Huru-hara.

141
00:12:04,015 --> 00:12:08,519
Sejak Spider hilang,
Silvermane menguasai bandar ini.

142
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:12,481
Jenayah berleluasa
dan polis pula ikut telunjuk Silvermane.

143
00:12:12,482 --> 00:12:13,774
Penduduk bandar ini…

144
00:12:13,775 --> 00:12:16,695
Mereka perlu seorang adiwira.

145
00:12:19,948 --> 00:12:23,284
Semoga mereka berjaya cari adiwira itu.

146
00:12:23,285 --> 00:12:26,121
- Dulu awak…
- Saya tahu dulu saya siapa.

147
00:12:28,665 --> 00:12:30,834
Saya juga tahu sekarang saya siapa.

148
00:12:31,585 --> 00:12:34,545
Orang macam Silvermane
akan selalu wujud, Robbie.

149
00:12:34,546 --> 00:12:36,173
Jangan buang masa melawan.

150
00:12:36,923 --> 00:12:38,883
Apakah yang Ruby akan fikir

151
00:12:38,884 --> 00:12:40,635
jika dia dengar awak cakap begitu?

152
00:12:53,315 --> 00:12:55,275
Dah lama Ruby meninggal

153
00:12:57,235 --> 00:12:59,821
dan saya tak peduli apa dia fikir.

154
00:13:03,992 --> 00:13:06,577
UNDI SEMULA DATUK BANDAR MORRIS
NADI NEW YORK

155
00:13:06,578 --> 00:13:08,954
Hai, Frankie. Awalnya awak hari ini.

156
00:13:08,955 --> 00:13:10,832
Hei, Reilly, apa khabar?

157
00:13:13,877 --> 00:13:16,670
Saya rajin berlatih helah saku saya.

158
00:13:16,671 --> 00:13:18,256
Ya? Ada kemajuan?

159
00:13:19,841 --> 00:13:21,009
Tengoklah.

160
00:13:24,930 --> 00:13:25,930
Gadis?

161
00:13:25,931 --> 00:13:28,849
- Apa yang awak tahu?
- Banyak. Saya cerdik.

162
00:13:28,850 --> 00:13:31,060
Jika begitu, awak patut bersekolah.

163
00:13:31,061 --> 00:13:33,604
Tak perlu. A tambah B sama dengan C.

164
00:13:33,605 --> 00:13:35,689
Jangan buat kira-kira dengan huruf.

165
00:13:35,690 --> 00:13:37,233
Donegal, Reilly.

166
00:13:37,234 --> 00:13:39,528
Kita patut bincang tentang semalam.

167
00:13:40,820 --> 00:13:43,197
<i>Jadi, apa yang awak nak bincang?</i>

168
00:13:43,198 --> 00:13:45,366
Kita biarkan seseorang mati semalam.

169
00:13:45,367 --> 00:13:47,743
Itu mungkin bawa masalah

170
00:13:47,744 --> 00:13:49,370
atau peluang keemasan.

171
00:13:49,371 --> 00:13:52,122
Apa pun, kita patut siasat
siapa yang upah kita

172
00:13:52,123 --> 00:13:54,084
dan kenapa mereka nak cari dia.

173
00:13:57,128 --> 00:13:58,296
Awak ada rancangan.

174
00:13:59,214 --> 00:14:00,422
Mungkin.

175
00:14:00,423 --> 00:14:03,008
Awak boleh hilang mabuk
sebelum 9.00 pagi esok?

176
00:14:03,009 --> 00:14:05,178
Hai, si kacak. Lama tak jumpa.

177
00:14:07,097 --> 00:14:08,390
Sebelum esok pagi?

178
00:14:09,432 --> 00:14:10,267
Sudah tentu.

179
00:14:11,685 --> 00:14:13,269
<i>Dapatkan edisi petang.</i>

180
00:14:13,270 --> 00:14:14,603
RUMAH SILVERMANE DIBAKAR!

181
00:14:14,604 --> 00:14:16,272
"Dia tinggal seluar dalam!"

182
00:14:16,273 --> 00:14:17,606
Terima kasih, encik.

183
00:14:17,607 --> 00:14:19,025
Berita terkini!

184
00:14:19,651 --> 00:14:22,027
<i>"Silvermane tinggal seluar dalam!"</i>

185
00:14:22,028 --> 00:14:24,321
<i>"Sejak Spider hilang,</i>

186
00:14:24,322 --> 00:14:27,283
<i>Silvermane menguasai bandar ini,</i>

187
00:14:27,284 --> 00:14:30,035
<i>membunuh sesiapa yang menghalangnya.</i>

188
00:14:30,036 --> 00:14:34,498
<i>Seseorang yang berani cuba bebaskan kita
daripada kuku besi Silvermane,</i>

189
00:14:34,499 --> 00:14:37,877
<i>membakar rumah dia
sewaktu dia tidur di dalamnya.</i>

190
00:14:38,712 --> 00:14:40,796
<i>Tapi Silvermane masih hidup.</i>

191
00:14:40,797 --> 00:14:44,718
<i>Jadi, bersedialah untuk pertumpahan darah
oleh Silvermane dan konconya.</i>

192
00:14:45,552 --> 00:14:49,680
<i>Kalaulah Spider masih ada
untuk selamatkan kita."</i>

193
00:14:49,681 --> 00:14:51,057
Alahai, Robbie.

194
00:14:51,683 --> 00:14:53,435
Tak habis-habis.

195
00:15:32,849 --> 00:15:35,351
Selamat petang, encik. Boleh saya bantu?

196
00:15:35,352 --> 00:15:38,020
Penghantaran untuk Boris Karloff.

197
00:15:38,021 --> 00:15:41,106
- Maaf, Karloff tak tinggal di sini.
- Dia tinggal di sini.

198
00:15:41,107 --> 00:15:44,861
Dia mungkin disenaraikan
di bawah nama pentasnya, Stein.

199
00:15:45,987 --> 00:15:48,782
Frank N. Stein.

200
00:15:51,868 --> 00:15:55,455
Baiklah, tak apa. Saya pergi dulu.

201
00:16:47,549 --> 00:16:49,926
- Awak tak perlu buat begitu.
- Saya tahu.

202
00:17:01,312 --> 00:17:02,522
Dah capai persetujuan.

203
00:17:05,108 --> 00:17:06,735
Kita rakan kongsi sekarang.

204
00:17:07,569 --> 00:17:10,320
Kita patut saling mengenali.

205
00:17:10,321 --> 00:17:14,533
- Tak, ini bukan apa yang kita… Tidak!
- Ayuh! Beri saya sesuatu.

206
00:17:14,534 --> 00:17:16,660
- Lepaskan saya!
- Mari sini.

207
00:17:16,661 --> 00:17:17,746
Mari sini.

208
00:17:24,377 --> 00:17:25,420
Biar betul?

209
00:17:36,681 --> 00:17:38,183
B. REILLY
PENYIASAT PERIBADI

210
00:17:43,062 --> 00:17:45,315
- Dia datang awal.
- Awak lewat!

211
00:17:46,274 --> 00:17:48,026
Pergi.

212
00:17:51,279 --> 00:17:52,279
Pagi, Winston.

213
00:17:52,280 --> 00:17:54,531
Nak secawan kopi atau teh?

214
00:17:54,532 --> 00:17:57,659
Atau pesan kedua-duanya
dan tengok mana sampai dulu?

215
00:17:57,660 --> 00:17:59,620
Tak payahlah, Reilly.

216
00:17:59,621 --> 00:18:02,664
Awak kata awak tahu di mana Addison.
Jadi, beritahu saya.

217
00:18:02,665 --> 00:18:04,917
Sebenarnya, harga dah naik.

218
00:18:04,918 --> 00:18:06,252
Apa?

219
00:18:07,170 --> 00:18:09,880
Penyiasat lain yang diupah
ditawarkan 50 dolar.

220
00:18:09,881 --> 00:18:12,425
Jadi, saya takkan beritahu
jika tiada 200 dolar.

221
00:18:13,009 --> 00:18:13,968
Pandainya.

222
